---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const updated = 'May 15, 2026';
---
<Base
  title="Privacy Policy | AIToolSpott"
  description="Privacy policy for AIToolSpott, including analytics, affiliate tracking, newsletter forms, advertising, and connected publishing integrations."
  slug="privacy"
>
  <Header />

  <main class="flex-1">
    <section class="border-b border-brand-border/50 py-14">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <p class="text-brand-cyan text-sm font-semibold mb-3">AIToolSpott</p>
        <h1 class="font-display font-extrabold text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-white mb-4">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-brand-dim leading-relaxed">
          Last updated: {updated}
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p>
          AIToolSpott publishes AI tool reviews, comparisons, guides, and connected creator
          content. This Privacy Policy explains what information we may collect, how we use it,
          and how third-party providers may process information when you visit the website,
          subscribe to updates, click affiliate links, or interact with connected publishing
          workflows.
        </p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          We may collect website usage information such as pages viewed, referral sources,
          approximate geographic region, browser type, device type, on-site events, and
          interaction metrics. If you submit information through a form, newsletter signup,
          creator workflow, or support contact, we may collect the information you provide,
          such as your email address and related metadata.
        </p>

        <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
        <p>
          We use information to understand site performance, improve content, measure traffic
          sources, operate newsletter forms, track affiliate link performance, serve or measure
          advertising, protect the site, diagnose technical issues, and improve our publishing
          and recommendation workflows.
        </p>

        <h2>Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          We may use analytics services, including Google Analytics, to measure aggregate
          website traffic and user behavior. These services may use cookies or similar
          technologies according to their own policies.
        </p>

        <h2>Affiliate Links and Attribution</h2>
        <p>
          Some links on AIToolSpott are affiliate links. If you click an affiliate link and
          make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. Affiliate
          partners may use cookies or tracking parameters to attribute referrals.
        </p>

        <h2>Advertising</h2>
        <p>
          We may display advertisements through third-party advertising providers, including
          Google AdSense or similar networks. Advertising providers may use cookies or related
          technologies to deliver, limit, or measure ads according to their own policies.
        </p>

        <h2>Connected Publishing Integrations</h2>
        <p>
          AIToolSpott may use connected platform integrations to distribute content or support
          creator workflows on services such as TikTok, YouTube, Pinterest, social platforms,
          affiliate networks, or other approved third-party systems. When authorized, these
          integrations may process limited account, publishing, or analytics data required to
          operate the intended workflow. We use such access only for the relevant operational
          purpose and in line with the connected platform's policies.
        </p>

        <h2>Newsletter</h2>
        <p>
          If you subscribe to a newsletter, your email address may be processed by our email
          service provider for subscription delivery, unsubscribe handling, and basic email
          analytics. You can unsubscribe using the link provided in emails.
        </p>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          This website and third-party services may use cookies, pixels, or similar technologies
          for analytics, affiliate attribution, security, and functionality.
        </p>

        <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell personal information. We may share limited information with service
          providers that help operate analytics, email delivery, affiliate tracking, hosting,
          and social publishing workflows.
        </p>

        <h2>Your Choices</h2>
        <p>
          You can disable cookies in your browser, unsubscribe from emails, or avoid submitting
          personal information through forms. Some website features may not work as expected if
          cookies are disabled.
        </p>

        <h2>Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We use reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect information, but no
          online system can be guaranteed to be completely secure.
        </p>

        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain information only for as long as reasonably necessary for analytics,
          operations, security, compliance, newsletter delivery, or legitimate business
          purposes, unless a longer retention period is required by law.
        </p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have rights to request access, correction,
          deletion, or restriction of personal information we hold about you. To make such a
          request, contact us through the official website or public brand channels.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy as the site, services, or connected platforms change.
          The latest version will be posted on this page.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For privacy questions, data requests, or policy concerns, contact AIToolSpott through
          the website or the official AIToolSpott public channels.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Base>
